  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the effect of daily use of Naproxen (a commonly
      used over-the-counter NSAID) on the physical performance of athletes, as measured by maximum
      oxygen consumption.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
